Death in the countryside
As it turned out, not only the city succumbed to the attack of the undead - the undead have taken over the entire area. First of all, you need to free the nearest village from the spawn of necromancy.
#subobj 1
Come to the village
The village which was attacked by the undead is located in the east of the area.
#subobj 2
Kill all the undead
The inhabitants are afraid to go out on the street, so you can destroy every creature you come across.